VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT didReceive\s+challenge.*useCredential|allowInvalidCertificates
WHEN EXPR MISSING:SecTrustEvaluate|SecTrustEvaluateWithError
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects certificate trust bypass indicators in network challenge handlers.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for SwiftUI Insecure Certificate Handling Marker.
